{
  "stem": "17301.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that would be a very bad thing to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they were trying to cover up a lot of it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, that was the Wehrmacht.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, the-- the regular German Army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, I hadn't seen an SS in our town at all, not at all.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were all Wehrmacht, Wehrmachts.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The living arrangement actually stayed on until we were ready to to be evacuated from there, which was in a Passover time in 1944.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at that time, they gave us two-days notice to get your stuff, whatever you want to get together and pack your bags, then because you will be taken out of your home.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "None at all, not whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not at all, not at all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no we didn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Actually, we didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because when they came in and they took us away from out of our house, you know, they took us into a place that-- it was a lumberyard.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they round up all the Jewish people in the lumber yard and naturally the accommodations were horrid.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were there for-- before we walked in, what happened was before, they searched us to make sure that we don't have any valuables on our bodies or hidden anywhere.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we, if we did anything, naturally, my mother handed over whatever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If she wore a ring, she had to hand it over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they searched even the young girls, I mean, bodily.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They searched them to make sure that they are not hiding any jewelry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were in this camp-- actually, camp, it was, it was a, a lumber yard-- for, for about a week or so.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was Passover time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And after a week, they decided to take us into another place, which was a brickyard.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
